comment: As Towns (MIN) sets the screen on Covington (PHI), Martin (MIN) and Covington make incidental contact with one another.
Wiggins (MIN) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Grant's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Okafor (PHI) was upheld and Minnesota was awarded possession.
Towns (MIN) sets the screen on Grant (PHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Covington (PHI) reaches in and makes contact with the ball on Wiggins' (MIN) play at the basket.
LaVine (MIN) and Canaan (PHI) engage on the inbound and the contact is incidental.
McConnell (PHI) reaches in and does not make contact with Wiggins' (MIN) arm and affect his shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) sets the screen on Covington (PHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Canaan (PHI) commits a take foul on Martin (MIN).
Martin (MIN) hand checks Covington (PHI) and affects his RSBQ on the perimeter.
Canaan (PHI) commits a take foul on LaVine (MIN).
